data.description: Two Story turn key home in beautiful Haynes Station features 4 bedrooms and 2.5 Bathrooms. This home boosts of Hardwood flooring in the foyer and open great room with stone surround fireplace. The kitchen is overlooking to great room and dining room for easy entertaining. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and a kitchen island with additional seating space. The dining room has large windows that allow for lots of natural light if desired. All bedrooms are large and located upstairs. Owner's suite has that dream walk in closet you have always wanted.! The Owner's bathroom features a double vanity sink, garden tub, and separate shower. Additional bedrooms also have spacious closets. Laundry room is located upstairs for your convenience. Washer and Dryer are 1 year old and will convey with the home. Additional full bath located upstairs with double sinks and shower/tub combo. The HVAC features Ultraviolet and ozone filtration to the ventilation system which eliminates odors and purifies the air. This helps greatly with allergies. There is a covered front porch with space for seating and a rear porch for grilling and entertaining. Backyard has privacy fence, automatic sprinklers, and sod. Neighborhood has a community pool, pravillion, streetlights, and sidewalks. Home is convenient to Fort Eisenhower, I-20, shopping, and dining.
